{"tid":604363,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嘅大學生越來越少，職訓局學生越來越多","createTime":"2018-03-24T15:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T09:10:01.000Z","uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f4d0c0d8c2887179e4f4f61d44b73f8ac68934","tid":604363,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"睇番而家香港大學讀天文、物理嘅學生買少見少， 仲有啲冷門( 搵唔到錢 )嘅學術科不斷被削減經費甚至收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我認為而家嘅香港三大只係高收入人士職訓局; 八大就變咗中收入人士職訓局，而樹中、鯨大就變咗自資職訓局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我咁講可能會以偏概全， 但係讀大學有幾多人真係為咗讀書學習而唔係為咗張沙紙同埋張嚟嘅人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好可惜呢個就係殘酷嘅現實，連我自己都冇得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醫生就係一個好好嘅例子， 有幾多人真係為咗純粹救人介意人工？<br />\n<br />\n製藥嘅又有幾多人係為咗杜絕絕症，而唔係為咗賺錢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 :讀緊自資職訓局"},{"pid":"a17dc027e7e187b2f665e736b36459762a074719","tid":604363,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"IVE呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba22b97ae5ce8a7d0fb146b990404318639a3058","tid":604363,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"IVE作育英才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d010f9d3cbc2a7cd58f4bf98ba50507dd7b96d68","tid":604363,"uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"三大出到黎都係搵萬幾蚊，其他你覺得會點"},{"pid":"6a7c30b0d7938d26d683ff0226c3689cdd0d662d","tid":604363,"uid":65012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"真係為讀書既都唔會係香港讀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而且要有錢"},{"pid":"4dd3807ed3a205e135ad4a74fb4e399b0e7ebac2","tid":604363,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote